lines.text: No, Pop. That's Gary Coleman, and watch what you say to him. You might get punched in your eye.
Punch me in my eye? I'll put him over my knee and give HIM a "different stroke".
I was reading in the trades the other day and they're looking for a young, hip, energetic black guy on 'Beverly Hills 90210'.
Shemales... Can't live with them, can't live without them.
